name: Project S.W.A.T v1.6
description:
Project S.W.A.T is a multiplayer first-person shooter focused on slower paced gameplay. The game is still very early in development, but now public beta is open!

The game features:

10 Maps (More to come!)

15+ Different weapons

Class customization

If you want to join our discord community, here is the link:https://discord.gg/BwxPA6AeXG

Keep up with the progress of the game:https://trello.com/b/emHC03nF/project-swat-progress
